"{\"uid\": \"cbc.ca-news-canada-montreal-olympic-basin-drowning-montreal-1.7285710\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A 20-year-old concertgoer is dead after drowning in the Olympic Basin at Montreal's Jean-Drapeau Park.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 73, \"end\": 81, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.246364887247156e-18, \"text\": \"Montreal\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\"}, {\"begin\": 84, \"end\": 96, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Drapeau_station\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jean-Drapeau\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Drapeau_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Drapeau_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Osheaga festival organizer Evenko confirmed in a statement that the victim attended the music festival and died after leaving the site Sunday.\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 131, \"end\": 137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evenko\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evenko\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evenko\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evenko\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Friends of the victim called 911 at about 7:45 p.m. on Sunday after he disappeared in the waters of the basin, which is a rowing, canoe-kayak and dragon boat venue on \\u00cele Notre-Dame that was built for the 1976 Montreal Summer Games.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Police and a firefighter nautical unit were deployed, and the young man's body was found in the water at about 9 p.m.\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Radio-Canada sources, the victim was visiting the city from Ontario.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 682